Shiloh - Operator (A Girl Like Me) [Promotional Single]


TITLE : Operator (A Girl Like Me)
ARTIST : Shiloh
ALBUM : Operator - Single
YEAR : 2006


Operator (A Girl Like Me) is the debut single by Canadian pop/rock  singer Shiloh. The song is about staying true to oneself and not becoming superficial.

"Operator (A Girl Like Me)" first debuted at No. 82 on the Canadian Hot 100 and peaked at No. 30, where it stayed for 1 week.
